aboutDescription: Hello! My name is Younseo and I am a Software Engineer from The University of California - San Diego. I will be graduating with my Bachelor's degree in Computer Science in May of 2021. The past years, I interned as a Technical Assistant and Software Engineer at Saline and Crown Sterling, and I cannot wait for my next journey. I'm most passionate about giving back to the community, and my goal is to pursue this passion within the field of software engineering!
